      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable daily driver that gets the job done without breaking the bank? This car is in fair condition and ready for its next adventure! While it shows some honest wear and tear from its years of service, it remains a dependable choice for anyone seeking practical transportation at a great value. It\u2019s a solid, functional vehicle that\u2019s perfect for commuting or as a first car!",
