      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it clearly shows its age and mileage. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some fading in the clear coat on the roof and hood. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a few small stains, and while the engine runs dependably, it may require some minor maintenance soon to keep it in peak shape. It's a solid, budget-friendly option for anyone needing a functional car that gets the job done without the premium price of a newer model.",
      "price": 21000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant attention from its next owner. The exterior shows noticeable rust, several dents, and fading paint, while the interior has heavy wear and some tears in the upholstery. Mechanically, the engine runs but has a persistent knock and an oil leak, and the suspension feels very loose. This would be an ideal candidate for a full restoration project or a source for parts, as it is not currently in reliable driving condition.",
      "price": 6000.0,
