    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just departed the showroom floor. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like gloss finish, entirely free of stone chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains a time capsule; the premium leather retains its original matte texture and fresh scent, with zero bolster wear or creasing. Every electronic component functions flawlessly, and the dashboard is pristine. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, backed by a comprehensive, folder-thick service history and recent preventative maintenance. It has been strictly garage-kept under a breathable cover and has never seen inclement weather. This is not just a well-kept car\u2014it is a meticulously preserved specimen for the most discerning enthusiast. Includes all original keys, manuals, and window sticker.",
      "price": 48500.0,
